{
  "stem": "20711.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he came and he stayed with far relatives in different location, and he was outside.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He never looked Jewish, and he just took a chance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Beside, by that time, there was no Jewish population in the country, and everybody was kind of sure there cannot be nobody, free Jewish.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And seeing a beautiful kid, like my brother was, nobody assumed any more.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The only thing, he had to be careful not to get into a situation when they would ask for his identity.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So as long as he stayed inside the house or just in a backyard, he was safe enough.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he also came to join us once he knew his family is in that cave.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he also came down, but he was also a lot of time upstairs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I had to wait till the Russians took over the town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was so ironical because the second day, we started to hear stories and screaming of girls and ladies, who was raped by the Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were terrible what they were doing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Nobody was safe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They got drunk during the night, and they had rampage through the city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So my uncle decided, back to the cave-- all the womenfolks back to the cave.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Even two neighboring beautiful daughters came with us until that first group of Russians passed through the town before the Russian authorities arrived, who had some control over the army.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We all had to go back to the cave for about two days, two extra days.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after that, we decided to go back to our village.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were so anxious to go back and see what happened to our home and to wait, when some other relatives may show up.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we couldn't wait any longer.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
